00:17:14,032 --> 00:17:15,159
JANTUNG MENGESANKAN

250
00:17:15,242 --> 00:17:17,453
Beginilah naga bisa terbang.

251
00:17:17,703 --> 00:17:19,204
Menarik.

252
00:17:19,830 --> 00:17:23,208
Pertama, potong kepalanya,
bersihkan perutnya, lalu lebarkan.

253
00:17:23,751 --> 00:17:24,793
Bantu aku, Mika.

254
00:17:25,335 --> 00:17:26,879
Aku akan buat saus rendamannya.

255
00:17:27,671 --> 00:17:28,505
Baiklah.

256
00:17:31,008 --> 00:17:32,760
Keahlian pisaumu mengesankan.

257
00:17:32,926 --> 00:17:36,221
Tak berbeda dari memotong naga lain.

258
00:17:36,889 --> 00:17:40,642
Minyak zaitun, lemon, garam, merica.

259
00:17:41,477 --> 00:17:45,064
Lalu tambahkan bumbu apa saja
yang ada di dapur kapal

260
00:17:45,147 --> 00:17:47,066
biarkan bumbu meresap 30 menit.

261
00:17:47,733 --> 00:17:49,109
Sudah.

262
00:17:53,989 --> 00:17:56,283
Tuangkan banyak minyak di wajan,

263
00:17:56,825 --> 00:17:59,411
lalu goreng dengan kulit menghadap
ke bawah.

264
00:18:04,124 --> 00:18:05,084
Aku tak sabar!

265
00:18:05,667 --> 00:18:08,879
Gunakan panci berisi air untuk menekannya.

266
00:18:11,048 --> 00:18:13,092
Balikkan begitu warnanya berubah.

267
00:18:13,550 --> 00:18:15,344
Lakukan yang sama di sisi lain

268
00:18:15,803 --> 00:18:17,930
lalu balikkan ke sisi kulit sekali lagi.

269
00:18:18,013 --> 00:18:19,807
Biarkan hingga kulitnya garing.

270
00:18:20,808 --> 00:18:21,850
Lalu, selesai.

271
00:18:22,476 --> 00:18:25,687
DRAGONET ALLA DIAVOLA

272
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:31,819
Baiklah, mari makan!

273
00:18:42,955 --> 00:18:44,915
Mika, kau bercanda, 'kan?

274
00:18:46,458 --> 00:18:47,334
Mika!

275
00:18:47,417 --> 00:18:48,502
Apakah beracun?

276
00:18:53,382 --> 00:18:54,216
Lezat sekali.

277
00:18:56,093 --> 00:18:56,969
Apa-apaan!

278
00:18:57,052 --> 00:18:58,762
Jangan buat kami takut begitu!

279
00:18:58,846 --> 00:18:59,680
Ini.

280
00:19:00,681 --> 00:19:01,974
Kita menangkapnya bersama.

281
00:19:15,571 --> 00:19:17,364
Enak sekali!

282
00:19:17,447 --> 00:19:22,035
Kulitnya sangat garing dan harum,
dan dagingnya lembut dan empuk!

283
00:19:22,119 --> 00:19:23,287
Enak.

284
00:19:23,704 --> 00:19:24,705
Biar kucoba.

285
00:19:25,497 --> 00:19:26,748
Kau serius?

286
00:19:27,165 --> 00:19:29,877
Kau serakah kalau soal makanan.

287
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,420
Itu tak benar!

288
00:19:31,503 --> 00:19:34,214
Kurasa pelajarannya adalah
jangan dibutakan keserakahan.

289
00:19:35,299 --> 00:19:37,801
Aku tak pernah dibutakan itu,
jadi aku tak tahu.

290
00:19:38,093 --> 00:19:40,012
Aku tak percaya.

291
00:19:40,345 --> 00:19:41,388
Aku tahu.

292
00:19:41,471 --> 00:19:43,515
Kubawakan separuh untuk Gibbs.

293
00:19:44,016 --> 00:19:48,020
Mika, kurasa kau dibutakan keserakahan.

294
00:19:48,103 --> 00:19:50,647
Tidak benar. Hei, jangan dibawa!

295
00:19:54,568 --> 00:19:55,402
Tunggu!

296
00:19:55,485 --> 00:19:56,737
Tidak!

297
00:19:58,447 --> 00:20:00,741
Kalian belum menemukan naganya?

298
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,951
Itu hadiah untuk Istana!

299
00:20:03,035 --> 00:20:07,456
Spesies miniatur sangat langka
untuk dipelihara di dalam rumah!

300
00:20:07,539 --> 00:20:09,875
Harganya dua miliar!

301
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:13,253
Kalian harus temukan!

302
00:20:15,505 --> 00:20:18,884
Menurutku naga itu tak beracun.

303
00:20:19,426 --> 00:20:23,013
Sakit kepala, meriang, menggigil,
dan demam.

304
00:20:23,263 --> 00:20:25,182
Itu gejala flu.

305
00:20:25,557 --> 00:20:26,391
Ya.

306
00:20:28,477 --> 00:20:30,312
Dia pasti kelelahan.

307
00:20:30,562 --> 00:20:35,233
Gibbs bekerja tanpa tidur atau istirahat.

308
00:20:36,443 --> 00:20:38,779
Gibbs selalu bekerja terlalu keras.

309
00:20:41,615 --> 00:20:42,616
Enak sekali!

310
00:20:47,996 --> 00:20:48,997
Lalu, kau.

311
00:20:50,207 --> 00:20:51,959
Jangan coba lakukan semuanya sendiri.

312
00:20:52,125 --> 00:20:55,587
Aku harus bekerja keras
untuk melunasi utangku.

313
00:20:56,755 --> 00:20:59,967
Omong-omong, kenapa kau bergabung
kapal ini?

314
00:21:06,056 --> 00:21:07,516
Aku punya alasan sendiri.

315
00:21:09,643 --> 00:21:11,770
Kau punya alasan sendiri?

316
00:21:12,896 --> 00:21:14,898
Itu masuk akal.

317
00:21:15,482 --> 00:21:16,525
Ya.

318
00:21:17,109 --> 00:21:18,110
Aku punya alasan.

319
00:21:20,112 --> 00:21:22,447
Namun rahasia tidak baik.

320
00:21:22,990 --> 00:21:23,949
Yah...

321
00:21:26,118 --> 00:21:29,538
- Untunglah mereka bersemangat.
- Kenapa itu penting?

322
